like":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年睇記得好似講過夢境既野一定要係現實見過<br />\n李安納度好似未見過對仔女 所以最後一幕見到對仔女個樣既話 應該係現實</blockquote><br />\n友人電影中還提出結局時 Cobb 看到子女的樣貌作為樂觀詮釋的證據之一，但筆者認為劇中沒明說明過 Cobb 不可以在夢中自行幻想子女的樣貌。反而，其實夢裏的大量行人都是由造夢者去幻想出來的，可見造夢者有能力幻想人物相貌，所以筆者認為這不能作為證據之一。"},{"pid":"ceadb705a5aee3be19f0272c0147786bdc6436dc","tid":501372,"uid":13325,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:03:38.000Z","msg":"對cobb黎講係唔係發緊夢已經唔重要"},{"pid":"4c64a443e9c13a8f3049ea3cb45b1b38151f24ab","tid":501372,"uid":27605,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:32:30.000Z","msg":"世界大戰抹黑宇宙了"},{"pid":"72f6df4b26b9f890452264124f74bc3d2da98281","tid":501372,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:34:59.000Z","msg":"套戲除左結尾<br />\n<br />\n邊個位好得過兇心人"},{"pid":"574796b83f099cf0cc405a27df11e8fb1c4565f8","tid":501372,"uid":65545,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13bf56c3e8467c0f6f1fae24d141bbf431ff54fa","tid":501372,"uid":128592,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實套戲最後有講 :&rdquo;it stopped &rdquo;</blockquote><br />\n最後個鐘頭影住 轉緊但又好似就停咁<br />\n然後就一野黑色 完左<br />\n唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af03f7ed21b5c2af825c5f656e8239700a037fe","tid":501372,"uid":47762,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實套戲最後有講 :&rdquo;it stopped &rdquo;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最後個鐘頭影住 轉緊但又好似就停咁<br />\n然後就一野黑色</span> 完左<br />\n唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n最後嘅對白係個女叫Cobb睇佢地起緊咩，Cobb問返佢地起緊咩，個仔話係喺懸崖上起左座樓（呼應返Cobb同Mal個夢世界嘅建築）